# -----------------
# API Base URL
# -----------------
# Optional: Override the API server URL
# If not set, defaults to window.location.origin (same-origin)

# For local development (uses same-origin by default):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000

# For production with separate client/server domains:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://server-production-96f7.up.railway.app

# IMPORTANT:
# - Leave unset for same-origin deployments (recommended)
# - Only set if client and server are on different domains
# - Must match server's PUBLIC_ORIGIN to avoid CORS errors
